title: Papa: Hemingway in Cuba. Official Movie Trailer #1 [HD] (2016)
description:
In theaters: April 29th, 2016

Description:

In 1959, a young journalist ventures to Havana, Cuba to meet his idol, the legendary Ernest Hemingway, who helps him find his literary voice while the Cuban Revolution comes to a boil around them. Based on a true story.

Director: Bob Yari

Writers: Denne Bart Petitclerc

Actors: Giovanni Ribisi, Adrian Sparks, Joely Richardson, Minka Kelly

Genre: Drama

Run Time: 1 hour 50 minutes
